z=x+iy
|z|^2 = x^2+y^2
|z+1|^2 = |z|^2+1 + 2x 
|z-1|^2 = |z|^2+1 - 2x
|z+1| = 4-|z-1|
|z+1|^2 = 16+|z-1|^2 - 8|z-1|.
4x = 16-8|z-1|
2|z-1| = 4-x
4|z-1|^2 = (4-x)^2
4|z|^2+4-8x = (4-x)^2
4(x^2+y^2)+4-8x = (4-x)^2,
3x^2+4y^2 = 12.
